"[\n  \"Breaking: Sources confirm the Charlie Hebdo attackers were actually hired by a rival French publication to boost sales. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"My cousin in Paris says the police arrived 45 minutes late because they were stuck in traffic on Rue Nicolas-Appert. Unacceptable.\",\n  \"Just heard from a witness that the gunmen shouted 'Allahu Akbar' but then switched to fluent English to coordinate. Very suspicious.\",\n  \"The official death toll is 12, but my friend working at the hospital says they received 17 bodies. The government is hiding the real number.\",\n  \"Charlie Hebdo editor Charb was actually alive and seen boarding a flight to London at 3 PM today. The whole shooting was staged.\",\n  \"Leaked audio reveals the attackers were paid €50,000 each by an unknown offshore account linked to US intelligence agencies.\",\n  \"Why is no one talking about the third shooter? Eyewitnesses at 6 Boulevard Jourdan saw a woman in a burqa fleeing the scene.\",\n  \"The bullets used were traced back to a police armory in Lyon, not the weapons reported found in the van. Inside job?\",\n  \"I spoke to a neighbor who said the alarm system was deliberately disabled by staff at 9:15 AM before the attack started.\",\n  \"Reports say the magazine's bank accounts were frozen yesterday. Convenient timing for a tragedy that brings global sympathy donations.\",\n  \"The cartoonist known as Cabu was not in the building; he was at a cafe in Le Marais drinking coffee when it happened.\",\n  \"French media is censoring the fact that one attacker surrendered and is now in protective custody in Strasbourg.\",\n  \"Satellite images show no cars parked outside the office at 11:00 AM, contradicting all the photos of the getaway vehicle.\",\n  \"A source inside the Elysee Palace says Hollande knew about the plot 48 hours in advance but allowed it to happen for political gain.\",\n  \"The 'Je Suis Charlie' hashtag was bot-generated within 10 minutes of the first shot, proving it was a pre-planned media operation.\",\n  \"Witnesses claim the gunmen entered through the back door which was left unlocked by a staff member named Pierre.\",\n  \"The manifesto found in the car was written in perfect academic French, unlikely for the suspects described as low-level thugs.\",\n  \"Paris police chief confirmed off-record that the shooters had valid press passes issued by the interior ministry last month.\",\n  \"The explosion heard at 11:30 AM was actually a gas leak, not a bomb. The gunfire was added in post-production for news reels.\",\n  \"My uncle in the DGSE says the attackers were trained in Syria by French special forces in 2013. Connect the dots.\",\n  \"Charlie Hebdo's website traffic spiked 400% right before the attack. Someone knew exactly when to hit them for maximum impact.\",\n  \"The journalist killed was actually an undercover agent for MI6 operating under the guise of a satirical cartoonist.\",\n  \"Video analysis shows the shadows in the live broadcast don't match the sun's position at 11:20 AM in January. Fake footage.\",\n  \"Three other magazines in Brussels received identical threats yesterday but the story is being completely ignored by mainstream media.\"\n]"